data.description: Home is now active under contract. If you'd still like to see it,  please give me a call or schedule through your agent.     This home is very spacious, is vacant, and in excellent condition. WELCOME HOME to this gorgeous MOVE-IN READY 2-story home in scenic Shirewood Park. You will sense the warm, inviting feeling of this stately home as soon as you pull in. Upon entering, you will immediately notice the classic solid oak flooring that speaks to the quality of craftsmanship that this home has to offer.  Enjoy updated lighting throughout. Brand New HVAC in 2023. Double stairway (1 front/1 rear) offers added safety and security as well as beauty. Half bath off of hall on main. To your left is the beautiful dining room. To your right, the front room displays a modern gas fireplace with a white brick surround and mantel. Going further, you will notice the custom built-in corner cabinetry and bookshelf. French doors invite you in to the sunroom with rear exit to the back yard. Roomy kitchen offers custom-built natural wood cabinetry with updated hardware, warm tile backsplash, matching dual wall oven, black glass cooktop, and stainless dishwasher. Cozy dinette area off kitchen leads to the bonus entertaining/serving area (complete with 2 sky lights) for extra space. Once again, french doors lead you into the enormous family room where you will relax and create memories. Upstairs you will find 5 spacious bedrooms, including the primary suite complete with covered balcony, and bathroom with stand-alone shower, soaking tub and vanity. Bedroom to rear of home also features full bath. Bedrooms are spacious and have natural oak flooring. Tons of closet space throughout. Second floor laundry. Finished garage with 2 bay doors and speckled paint floor. Privacy fence lines the back yard perimeter. Quiet setting for you and yours to enjoy. Visit nearby Lake Kedron and Blue Smoke Park. Almost endless dining and entertainment options, miles of golf cart paths, all within award-winning McIntosh School district.
